{"tid":1027506,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合國計劃修訂草案，將二次元作品包含於兒童色情定義上","createTime":"2019-02-19T00:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T05:36:26.000Z","uid":64191,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fb82d41f02ea997631458acd337ce542763afb3a","tid":1027506,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:49:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ohchr.org/EN/HRBodies/CRC/Pages/DraftGuidelinesOPs.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2FEN%2FHRBodies%2FCRC%2FPages%2FDraftGuidelinesOPs.aspx&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEu%2FcXzH0lQqBACTLtzCSRXY%3D&h=edd617df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ohchr.org/EN/HRBodies/CRC/Pages/DraftGuidelinesOPs.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n最近聯合國對兒童權利公約，釋出最新解釋草案，計劃將二次元創作亦包含於兒童色情管制，詳細如下：<br />\n<br />\n61. Child pornographyis defined in article 2 OPSCas &ldquo;any representation of a child engaged in real or simulated explicit sexual activities, regardless ofthe means used, or any representation of the sexual parts of a child for<br />\nprimarily sexual purposes&rdquo;. The qualification &ldquo;by whatever means&rdquo; reflects the broad range of material available in a variety of media, online and offline<span style=\"color: red;\">. It includes, inter alia: visual material such as photographs, movies, drawings and cartoons; audio representations; any digital media representation; live performances; written materials in print or online; andphysical objects such as sculptures, toys, or ornaments.</span><br />\n<br />\n63.  The Committee is of the view that &ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">simulated explicit sexual activities&rdquo; should be interpreted as including any material, online or offline,</span> that depicts or otherwise represents any person appearing to be a child engaged in real or simulated sexually explicit conduct and realistic and/or virtual depictions of a child engaged in sexually explicit conduct. <span style=\"color: red;\">Such depictions<br />\ncontribute to normalising the sexualisation of children and fuels the demand of child sexual abuse material.</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個草案將定義涵蓋到二次元動畫、漫畫、Vtuber、玩具、畫作等創作，而立呢個草案既原因，聯合國係認為只要有人鍾意睇蘿莉、正太作品，就會變得想搞或虐待未成年人。<br />\n<br />\n但最大問題，係草案既解釋上，63條就指「看似係同兒童色情有關」去定義，但西方人既標準係點？係好暴走既，今次雖然只係草案，但已經震驚成個二次元界"},{"pid":"8c2da556e323155f15751bdbe7b872985e35dcd9","tid":1027506,"uid":1524,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:56:27.000Z","msg":"漫畫嘅嘢好難界定wo，佢角色設定係千年不老童顏但係細細粒咁點搞？"},{"pid":"59c0cc1d4719f0c64433b89d7c0afd3d1b4ab700","tid":1027506,"uid":237562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c2da556e323155f15751bdbe7b872985e35dcd9","tid":1027506,"uid":1524,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:56:27.000Z","msg":"漫畫嘅嘢好難界定wo，佢角色設定係千年不老童顏但係細細粒咁點搞？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:58:00.000Z","msg":"虛竹大戰天山童姥"},{"pid":"67b75df2915e0f01f7ae0141c428de82e62e8a8e","tid":1027506,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:58:11.000Z","msg":"h動睇多真大獲"},{"pid":"3ed9fa8fe90041f0d59d37dbd874abb4ecc7fbe1","tid":1027506,"uid":64191,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"59c0cc1d4719f0c64433b89d7c0afd3d1b4ab700","tid":1027506,"uid":237562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c2da556e323155f15751bdbe7b872985e35dcd9","tid":1027506,"uid":1524,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:56:27.000Z","msg":"漫畫嘅嘢好難界定wo，佢角色設定係千年不老童顏但係細細粒咁點搞？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:58:00.000Z","msg":"虛竹大戰天山童姥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:58:57.000Z","msg":"佢個範圍講明外型似兒童就唔得"},{"pid":"23de56f65532330ec82010f886147c80b59919b3","tid":1027506,"uid":155732,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:59:33.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106f87ed879bb84b542b257ce2eb5ff2fba7c5d8","tid":1027506,"uid":28279,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime